<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="addiction-n">addiction <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'dɪkʃn/    美 /əˈdɪkʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u-c">1.★ <strong>[U] &amp; [C]上瘾；热衷：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>drug / alcohol / Internet / online shopping addiction</strong>
毒瘾/酒瘾/网瘾/网购瘾</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She kicked her three-pack-a-day cigarette habit, and overcame her <strong>addiction to</strong> alcohol. 
她改掉了一天三包烟的恶习，并戒掉了酒瘾。</p><footer>2010 湖南改</footer></div></div>